[5.283, "o", "\u001b[0m189 of 230 patients carry an E85.x amyloidosis code. I notice data-quality issues: inconsis\u2026\r\n"]
[5.65, "o", "\u001b[38;5;78m  \u270e register_question\u001b[0m \u001b[2mL4 spawned\u001b[0m Among E85.x amyloidosis patients, what is the balance of cardiac phenotype (cardiom\u2026\r\n"]
