[6.317, "o", "\u001b[0mCardiac phenotype dominates (155/189, 82%) with substantial neuro overlap. Let me verify ag\u2026\r\n"]
[6.683, "o", "\u001b[38;5;75m  \u2699 run_analysis\u001b[0m \u001b[38;5;245mimport re\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[7.017, "o", "\u001b[38;5;80m  \ud83d\udd0d web_search\u001b[0m \u001b[38;5;245mhereditary ATTR amyloidosis cardiac versus neuropathic phenotype prop\u2026\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[7.35, "o", "\u001b[0mThe literature confirms ATTRv presents as cardiac-predominant, neuropathic-predominant, or \u2026\r\n"]
[7.717, "o", "\u001b[38;5;75m  \u2699 run_analysis\u001b[0m \u001b[38;5;245me85_ids=set(dx[dx['dx ICD code'].astype(str).str.upper().str.startswith('E85'\u2026\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[8.05, "o", "\u001b[0mThe 41 \"non-E85\" patients still have amyloidosis by name \u2014 a coding-inconsistency signal. L\u2026\r\n"]
[8.417, "o", "\u001b[38;5;75m  \u2699 run_analysis\u001b[0m \u001b[38;5;245me85_ids=set(dx[dx['dx ICD code'].astype(str).str.upper().str.startswith('E85'\u2026\u001b[0m\r\n"]
