[9.383, "o", "\u001b[0mI've completed the characterization of cohort A's TTR/ATTR amyloidosis population. Here's t\u2026\r\n"]
[9.75, "o", "\u001b[0mpredominantly neuropathic, predominantly cardiac, or mixed (exhibiting both polyneuropathy \u2026\r\n"]
